description: Lovely updated single family home featuring an open floor plan with beautiful hardwood floors, an island, first floor bathroom and laundry, private back patio, 3 bedrooms plus an office, and a parking space. The well designed floor plan offers two bedrooms and a full bath on the second floor and a large third-floor suite with another full bath. There's plenty of storage in the basement. This location is ideal: easy access to Rte. 93/90 and Logan Airport, a short walk to Andrew Sq. Red Line, Moakley Playground and Park, Carson Beach, Tatte Bakery, Broadway and great restaurants. Nest Thermostat, cameras and front door lock are an added bonus. Come take a look, and make this place your next home! Open houses Saturday and Sunday 11:00 – 12:30.
